  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ザ・グレイトバトルPOCKETは、アルファユニットが開発し、バンプレストが発売した雑多なゲームで、1999年に日本でリリースされました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The Great Battle Pocket is a classic game for the Game Boy Color platform. It offers exciting action, strategy, and role-playing elements to keep players engaged. With its captivating storyline and challenging gameplay, players can expect an immersive experience as they navigate through various levels. The game allows you to control a variety of characters and engage in epic battles against formidable enemies. Overall, The Great Battle Pocket delivers a thrilling gaming experience that combines multiple genres seamlessly.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
